    "description": "We are committed to maximizing the protection of your personal information when using QRTable's services. This policy explains in detail how we collect, use, store, protect, and share your data, as well as your rights and choices regarding your personal information.",
    "infoTitle": "Information We Collect",
    "infoContent": "When you use our services, we may collect the following types of information: \n- Personal identification information such as full name, email address, phone number, and contact address.\n- Login and security information such as password and login history.\n- Order information, transaction history, payment methods.\n- Technical data such as IP address, device type, browser, access time, pages viewed.\n- Feedback, reviews, and support contact information from you.\nWe only collect the information necessary to serve the purpose of using the service and to comply with legal regulations.",
    "usageTitle": "How We Use Information",
    "usageContent": "Your personal information is used for the following purposes: \n- Processing and managing orders, transactions, and payments.\n- Improving service quality and optimizing user experience.\n- Sending notifications, updates, promotions, or information related to the service.\n- Customer support, resolving complaints, responding to requests.\n- Fulfilling legal requirements, audits, and fraud prevention.\nWe do not use personal information for external advertising purposes or share it with unrelated third parties, except with your consent or as required by law.",
    "securityTitle": "Data Security and Storage",
    "securityContent": "We apply physical, technical, and administrative security measures to protect personal data from unauthorized access, loss, alteration, or disclosure.\n- Data is encrypted during transmission and storage on secure systems.\n- Only authorized personnel have access to personal information.\n- Regularly inspect and update security systems to prevent risks.\n- Data is stored for the necessary period for service use and in compliance with legal regulations.\nIf a security incident is detected, we will promptly notify you and the authorities as required."
  },
